type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-45_">What is a sublimation printer? Sublimation printer is used for special types of printing, not regular black and white documents. Ever wonder how t-shirts get such vibrant colorful prints on them? Or maybe you want to customize a mug or a wooden frame? To get a better understanding of sublimation printers and printing, compare them to normal printers.</span></p><h5 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-60_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-59_"><span style="font-weight: 700;">Printing Art</span><br></span></h5><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-78_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-77_">You may be more familiar with regular printers or inkjet printers. It uses an ink-dot technique to place ink on paper. At the same time, sublimation printers penetrate ink vapor into their media.Depending on the printer you use, most sublimation prints also need to go through a heat press. For inkjet printers, the documents delivered are complete. But for sublimation printers, you need to heat press the sublimation paper with the media of your choice</span></p><h5 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-75_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-74_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Ink</span></span></h5><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-81_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-80_">Regular printers usually use ink cartridges. These contain liquid, and you can even see that it's still wet when a normal printer delivers the document. Sublimation printers use a special type of ink called dye-sublimation ink. This dye ink turns into a gas or vapor when transferred.</span></p><h5 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-hOGkXu eBgidd pf-72_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-gUQvok zBuIu pf-71_"><span style="font-weight: bold;">Output</span></span></h5><p class="sc-eGPXGI dCeUID pf-84_" data